Package: cbenefit
Title: Cross Validated C-Index and C-Index for Benefit 
Version: 0.2.2
Author: Theodor Adrian Balan, David van Klaveren
Maintainer: Theodor Adrian Balan <hello@tbalan.com>
Description: Calculates cross-validated the c-index (or c-statistic) and the c-for-benefit of van Klaveren et al.<10.1016/j.jclinepi.2017.10.021> for Cox proportional hazards and logistic regression models. Calibration and net befit plotting functions are provided. Ridge and LASSO penalties are supported via the glmnet package. 
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: Hmisc, MatchIt, dplyr, ggplot2, glmnet, magrittr, rlang, survival, tibble, broom
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
URL: https://github.com/tbalan/cbenefit
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    egg,
    pander,
    rms
VignetteBuilder: knitr
